channel.description: Recent content in Holt County|Nebraska|United States on Roadsign Pictures

item.title: US-20 West/NE-11 North at US-20/NE-11 Split
item.description: US-20 West/NE-11 North at US-20/NE-11 split in Atkinson.

item.title: US-20 West at NE-11 - Atkinson
item.description: US-20 West at NE-11 in Atkinson. Use NE-11 South to Burwell. Continue west on US-20 to Bassett. NE-11 North joins US-20 west through Atkinson.

item.title: US-20 West Approaching NE-11
item.description: US-20 West approaching NE-11 in Atkinson. NE-11 North joins US-20 West through Atkinson.

item.title: US-20 West/US-281 North at US-20/US-281 Split
item.description: US-20 West/US-281 North at US-20/US-281 split in O’Neill.

item.title: US-20 West/End US-275 West at US-281
item.description: US-20 West/End US-275 West at US-281 in O’Neill. US-281 North joins US-20 West through O’Neill.

item.title: US-20/US-275 West Approaching US-281
item.description: US-20/US-275 West approaching US-281 in O’Neill. This is the western terminus of US-275.

item.title: US-20/US-275 West - O'Neill
item.description: Entering O’Neill on US-20/US-275 West. O’Neill is the county seat of Holt County. A historic US-20 route marker is also displayed below the city limit sign. This marker is seen along US-20 in central and western Nebraska.

item.title: US-20/US-275 West - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance Marker on US-20/US-275 West. Distance to O’Neill and Ainsworth. O’Neill has been the control city from Sioux City, Iowa on US-20 westbound. Ainsworth is the control city west from O’Neill to Ainsworth.

item.title: US-20 West at US-275
item.description: US-20 West at US-275 in Holt County. US-275 West joins US-20 westbound.

item.title: US-20 West Approaching US-275
item.description: US-20 West approaching US-275 in Holt County. Use US-275 East to Ewing; use US-20/US-275 West to O’Neill.

item.title: US-20 West Approaching US-275
item.description: US-20 West approaching US-275 in Holt County. US-275 West joins US-20 west to O’Neill.

item.title: US-20 West - Distance Marker
item.description: Distance marker on US-20 west. Distance to Inman and O’Neill.

item.title: US-20 West Approaching NE-45A Spur
item.description: US-20 West approaching NE-45A Spur in Holt County.

item.title: US-20 West at NE-45B Link South
item.description: US-20 West at NE-45B Link South to Ewing. Continue west on US-20 for O’Neill.

item.title: US-20 West Approaching NE-45B Link
item.description: US-20 West approaching NE-45B Link in Holt County.
